Imagine that you are doing a project on how the pandemic has changed eating habits in Zetland. You have found some data on the subject - the results of the opinion polls (see the diagram below).
Comment on the data in the diagram and give your opinion on the subject of the project.

How the pandemic has changed eating habits

Write 200-250 words.

Use the following plan:
- make an opening statement on the subject of the project;
- select and report 2-3 facts;
- make 1-2 comparisons where relevant;
- outline a problem that can arise with eating habits and suggest a way of solving it;
- conclude by giving your opinion on the role of eating habits in our lives.
